# Observability — Lean Metrics
- **Latency SLOs**: p95 < 2s, p99 < 5s for chat responses.
- **Error budget**: <2% 5xx errors in 1h window.
- **Metrics to track**:
  - Tokens in/out per request.
  - Latency per LLM call and MCP tool call.
  - Cache hits/misses (if Redis enabled).
- **Logs**: Redact secrets/PII. Include request id + coarse timings only.
- **Alerting**: Future → GitHub/Discord webhook integration on sustained errors.
